fields.name: YMCA
fields.description:
For more than 130 years, the YMCA of Middle Tennessee has sought to strengthen the foundations of our community and nurture the potential of the men, women and children who call our region home. The YMCA's vision is to offer Hope for Life to people of all ages, faiths, races, backgrounds and abilities, regardless of their socio-economic circumstances. Through a range of relationship-focused, impactful programs, services, partnerships and collaborations, we will offer hope throughout Middle Tennessee and southern Kentucky by:

 - Inspiring Youth
 - Improving Health
 - Serving Others
 - Creating Community

Through all they do, YMCA of Middle Tennessee is guided by their core character values: Caring, Honesty, Respect and Responsibility.
